    "en": {
      "title": "Pfizer Vaccine Expiry Extension",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the Ministry of Health, the expiry date of the Pfizer vaccine has been extended based on the recommendations of the World Health Organization.",
        "According to a statement issued by the Ministry of Health, the expiry date of the Pfizer vaccine has been extended as per the recommendation of the distribution division of the World Health Organization and UNICEF.",
        "Accordingly, the ministry has announced that the expiry period of vaccines stored at 90-60 degrees Celsius will be extended from 9 to 12 months.",
        "Meanwhile, the General Secretary of the Government Medical Officers Association, Haritha Aluthge, said that the number of reported corona patients in Sri Lanka has increased.",
        "According to the announcement of the Government Information Department, 72 corona infections and 02 corona deaths have been reported the day before yesterday."
      ],
